{"tid":1568971,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"原來催淚彈嘅辣椒素水平同而家世界上最辣嘅辣椒有得fight","createTime":"2019-09-14T12:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T12:37:43.000Z","uid":64694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0992e8040d67ed1d299065c3b9c5c2c1fe9bd4ac","tid":1568971,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:37:20.000Z","msg":"史高維爾指標係一種量度辣度嘅指標，其中紅色圈住嘅係催淚彈嘅指標，可以睇吓佢同其他辣椒嘅水平比較，綠色圈住嘅龍之氣息係現時世界上最辣椒（我估上面嗰啲應該已經唔係可食用嘅辣椒嚟）、藍色圈住嘅係哈瓦那辣椒（喺龍之氣息被發現之前曾經係世界上最辣嘅辣椒）、紫色圈住嘅係平時都講嘅指天椒，所以基本上催淚彈所辣度（刺激度）係同世界上最辣嘅辣椒差唔多，甚至超過添<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Fkt0J1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Fkt0J1.jpg&h=3045f06f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%8F%B2%E9%AB%98%E7%B6%AD%E7%88%BE%E6%8C%87%E6%A8%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%258F%25B2%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E7%2588%25BE%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25A8%2599&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXSsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=81bf982c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%8F%B2%E9%AB%98%E7%B6%AD%E7%88%BE%E6%8C%87%E6%A8%99</a>"},{"pid":"976c84b2ff907f320dd06a3ca3e96b863733539c","tid":1568971,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:37:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}